Detailed Description

An abstract class which implements common behaviors of list-based collections.

This class has a single instance variable on which all the implemented methods act, and also conforms to several protocols:

  • NSCoding
  • NSCopying
  • NSFastEnumeration

Rather than enforcing that this class be abstract, the contract is implied.
